# SiteLens API env files (do not put secrets in this file).
#
# Local (Docker PostGIS/Redis):
#   cp .env.local.example .env.local
#
# Production reference + verify script (Fly uses `fly secrets set`):
#   cp .env.production.example .env.production
#
# Loader: src/loadEnv.ts picks `.env.local` unless NODE_ENV/APP_ENV=production
# (then `.env.production`). Override with DOTENV_CONFIG_PATH=/path/to/file.
